sequenceDiagram
  participant U as Admin (Frontend)
  participant AUTH as API Auth
  participant USERS as API Users
  participant HACK as API Hackathons
  participant DB as MongoDB

  U->>AUTH: POST /api/auth/login (email)
  AUTH->>DB: find User by email
  DB-->>AUTH: role admin
  AUTH-->>U: role detecte

  U->>AUTH: POST /api/auth/credentials (email, password)
  AUTH->>DB: verify passwordHash
  DB-->>AUTH: user valide
  AUTH-->>U: JWT session + user

  U->>USERS: GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /api/users
  USERS->>DB: read/write users
  DB-->>USERS: users updated
  USERS-->>U: 200/201 success

  U->>HACK: GET/POST/PATCH/DELETE /api/hackathons
  HACK->>DB: read/write hackathons
  DB-->>HACK: hackathons updated
  HACK-->>U: 200/201/204 success
